### Game Summary — Men's
# Fetches the full box score and game details for a specific ESPN event.
# Useful for verifying that winner/loser data is correct after games complete.
# Replace {eventId} with an ID found in the scoreboard response (events[].id).
#
# Example usage:
#   1. Run a scoreboard request from espn-scoreboard.http
#   2. Copy an event ID from events[].id
#   3. Paste it into the URL below and run

GET https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/basketball/mens-college-basketball/summary?event={eventId}
Accept: application/json

###

### Game Summary — Women's

GET https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/basketball/womens-college-basketball/summary?event={eventId}
Accept: application/json

